# Investment Frameworks (decision tree)

Do **not** read every file under `_system/frameworks/`. Use the tree below.

## Always (every research task)

1. `_system/frameworks/decision_stack.md` — six questions; stance flow  
2. `_system/frameworks/deep_dive_structure.md` — section order  
3. `_system/frameworks/report_prose.md` — plain English, ledger at end  
4. `_system/frameworks/option_treatment.md` — option scan; no auto-zero  
5. `{TICKER}/research/valuation.json` + trigger map in `_system/frameworks/classification.md`  

## Triggered only (from valuation.json / classification)

Open **only** rows that apply — index in `_system/frameworks/analysis_arsenal.md`:

| Trigger | Read |
|---------|------|
| `payoff_lens: asset` or `valuation_mode: optionality` | `optionality_valuation.md` |
| `evidence_refresh.type` set | Same file → § **Mechanical refresh and market inputs** |
| `segment_build` / segment overlay | `segment_cashflow_valuation.md` |
| `ai_overlay` | `ai_infrastructure_valuation.md` |
| `payoff_lens: event` | `special_situation_lens.md` |
| `payoff_lens: levered` | `equity_stub_valuation.md` |
| Holdco book roll-forward | `current_book_estimate.md` |
| HK-indexed ticker | `hk_cross_reference.md` |
| Third party / cross-check | `third_party_cross_reference.md`, `third_party_sources.md` |
| Valuation section prose | `archetype_valuation_prose.md`, `irr_assumption_ledger.md`, `lawrence_irr.md` § F |
| MOI comprehensive pass | `moi_company_evaluation.md` (onboard / idea funnel only) |

## Mechanical pipeline (one command)

```bash
python _system/scripts/marvin_cloud_refresh.py {TICKER} --date YYYY-MM-DD
```

Batch: `batch_portfolio_refresh.py`. QA: `make research-check TICKER={TICKER}`.

Do **not** duplicate substeps from `cloud_marvin_runbook.md` unless debugging.

## Wisdom library

`_system/reference/investment-wisdom/` — cite PDFs when applying a triggered mental model; not a mandatory read list.

## New framework files

Forbidden without `framework_governance.md` checklist + `_system/prompts/architecture_review_template.md` proposal.

Moved stubs: `evidence_refresh.md`, `market_inputs_freshness.md` → `optionality_valuation.md` § Mechanical refresh.
